data.description: This lovely updated ranch style home is ready for new owners! It has a great floor plan with open concept kitchen and big center island. New carpet throughout. Central air conditioning and main level laundry. Home has 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Master bedroom has private bathroom with walk-in shower. and double sinks. Dining room has doors out to rear covered patio. Backyard has mature landscape and bleck fence. There is a 2-car garage and expanded driveway perfect for RV parking. VA Assumable Mortgage. Buyers must qualify. A must see home! CALL TODAY for your personal showing
